title: Ravens-Rams MNF Preview, Potential shakeups for Cowboys and Panthers (Football 11/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Ravens vs Rams on Monday Night Football (3:00). The guys discuss how to slow Lamar Jackson and why Los Angeles' offense has taken such a step back before they decide on player props and pick the game. Then, Jason La Canfora joins the podcast to analyze what happens next in Dallas (30:15), why Carolina could be headed for change as well (39:00), Ryan Tannehill earning a payday this offseason and more on the 2020 QB market (51:00).
